.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aJapanisch. 4aLyman, Benjamin Smith. 4aMorphophonologie. 4aRendaku. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aJapanese.  aLyman, Benjamin Smith.  aMorphonology.  aMorphophonemics.  aRendaku.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishz978311099370708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022z9783110993684oZDB-23-DSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMouton eBook Package 2022z97831107912970 cEPUBz97831107552370 cprintz978311075501540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311075510740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110755107423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110755107/original  a978-3-11-079129-7  Mouton eBook Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099370-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSPb2022